(39, 'lashes', 'PARTY LASHES', '202303290937party-lashes-11.jpg', 'Party Lashes', 'Party lashes are made up of cluster fans with multiple lashes on each bulb. They are applied on the top of your natural lashes, providing you a fancy yet natural look.', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 27px; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold;\">What are the benefits of Party Lashes?</b></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><li>Cluster lashes are a quick process resulting in instant volumized lashes</li><li>Party Lashes feels natural and weightless</li><li>The treatments procedure is relaxing and comfortable</li><li>The treatment provides extra length to your natural lashes</li></ul>', '<p><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">1. Is there anything I need to do before my lash treatment? (Pre-care)</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A.</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><li>Clean your lashes before your scheduled appointment</li><li>Avoid using oil-based products on and around the eye area before your appointment.</li><li>Get a shower before your appointment as you will not be suggested to get the lashes wet at all for 24 hours after your treatment</li><li>You must remove your contact lenses during the process and therefore, don’t forget to bring your case and solution with you</li></ul><p><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">2. How long do Party Lashes last for?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Ideally, they can last up to 7 to 10 days. But it depends on the condition of your natural lashes, the natural oil production in the eye area and on your post-treatment care.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">3. How long will this treatment take?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Your appointment will take approximately 20 to 30 minutes.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">4. Do I need a patch test for this treatment?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. You do not require a patch test for party lashes as per the used glue guidelines. The glue used is skin sensitive.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">5. Does this hurt?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. No, this is a relaxing process. You just have to close your eyes during the treatment.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">5. I wear contact lenses. Can I have this treatment done?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Yes, this is suitable for you. Although we do recommend you remove your lenses during the treatment.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">6. Can I apply mascara on these lashes?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Applying mascara on the bottom lashes give a dramatic look. However, if you do not apply any products on your party lashes, they can stay longer.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">7. Can I get the lashes wet?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. After 24 hours you can. But if the lashes get wet, it will be hard to maintain its curl and shape.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">8. . I have an eye infection. Is this treatment suitable for me?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. If you are suffering from any eye infection, you shouldn’t undergo this treatment. If you have a stye or other infection, inside or at the edge of your eyelid, they can become inflamed and painful due to this treatment. You should inform your therapist beforehand about any such concern and seek medical advice before undergoing any treatment.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">9. What should I do after my treatment? Are there any restrictions? (Aftercare)</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A.</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><li>For 48 hours avoid sauna, steam, showers, or hot baths</li><li>Please be gentle with your lashes</li><li>Avoid using oil-based products in the eye area and please do not rub or pull your lashes out</li><li>Do not use waterproof mascara or make up remover as this will affect the bonding of the lashes</li><li>Never pull off the eyelash extensions as this will pull out your natural lashes too</li><li>Be gentle with the extensions and avoid tugging and getting them caught on clothes and towels</li></ul>', '2023-03-29 09:37:36', '2023-03-29 09:37:36'),
(40, 'lashes', 'SEMI PERMANENT NATURAL & GLAMOUR LASHES', '202303290949aftercare7.jpg', 'Semi Permanent Lashes', 'In Semi-Permanent lashes, one extension is applied to one natural lash using a special adhesive. These lashes fall out only with your natural hair growth cycle and they can last up to 6 weeks with maintenance. Semi-Permanent Lashes are light weight, and they can result in achieving a fuller but natural enhancement or a dramatic look.', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 27px; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold;\">What are the benefits of semi-permanent lashes?</b></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><li>Semi-Permanent Lashes transform your natural lashes into longer, thicker, and curlier lashes</li><li>Semi-Permanent Lashes are appropriate for special occasions and holidays or if you want a natural enhancement</li><li>If you want to avoid wearing mascara every day, this treatment is for you. It helps you to say no to clumping, and smudging mascara</li><li>It can be your best choice if you would like a natural or full-on glam look. With maintenance these lashes can last several weeks</li></ul>', '<p><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">1. Is there anything I need to do before my treatment? (Pre-care)</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A.</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><li>We highly recommend you to clean your lashes before arriving for your scheduled appointment</li><li>Please avoid using oil-based products on and around the eye area</li><li>Get a shower before your appointment as you will not be suggested to get the lashes wet at all for 24 hours after your treatment</li><li>If you use contact lenses, you will be asked to remove them during your treatment and therefore, don’t forget to bring your lens case and solution with you</li></ul><p><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">2. How old must I be to have this done?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. From age of 16+ you can receive this service.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">3. How long do Semi Permanent lashes last?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Ideally, they last up to 2 to 3 weeks, depending on the condition of your natural lashes, your post-treatment cleanliness/ care, and the natural oil production of the eye area. We recommend to refill lashes, every 2 weeks for long lasting results.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">4. How long will this treatment take?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Your appointment will take approximately 45 to 60 minutes, if you opt for the glamour look this will take longer than the usual time stated above.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">5. Do I need a patch test?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Yes , if you have not had semi permanent lashes or Russian lashes done from us before , you are required to come for a patch test 24/48 hours prior to your appointment. If you are a regular client and we have your semi permanent lash or Russian lash extension history within 6 months registered in our system, you do not require a patch test if there is no change in your medical history.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">6. I don’t want my lashes to be too long. Is this suitable for me?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Yes, this is suitable for you as semi-permanent lashes come in all lengths. Therefore, you can choose to have a fuller but natural length.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">7. I wear contact lenses. Can I have this done?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Yes, this is suitable for you. Although we do recommend you removing your lenses for the duration of the treatment.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">8. Can I apply mascara on these lashes?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Applying mascara can give you a dramatic look, however if you do not apply any products on your lashes, they can last longer.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">9. Does this hurt?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. No. Eyelash extensions is a closed eye treatment; you should feel relaxed during the process.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">10. Can I get the lashes wet?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Try not to get your lashes wet. Once the lashes get wet, it will be hard to maintain its curl and shape.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">11. I have an eye infection is this suitable for me?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. If you are suffering from any eye infection, you shouldn’t undergo this treatment. If you have a stye or other infection, inside or at the edge of your eyelid, they can become inflamed and painful due to this treatment. You should inform your therapist beforehand about any such concern and seek medical advice before undergoing any treatment.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">12. What should I do after my treatment? are there any restrictions? (Aftercare)</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A.</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><li>For 48 hours avoid sauna, steam, showers, or hot baths</li><li>Please be gentle with your lashes</li><li>Please avoid using oil-based products on the eye area</li><li>Please do not rub or pull your lashes out</li><li>Do not use waterproof mascara or make up remover as this will affect the bonding of the lashes</li><li>Never pull off the eyelash extensions as this will pull out your natural lashes too</li><li>Be gentle with the extensions and avoid tugging and getting them caught on clothes and towels</li></ul>', '2023-03-29 09:49:02', '2023-03-29 09:49:02'),
(41, 'lashes', 'RUSSIAN NATURAL & GLAMOUR LASHES', '202303290951russian-lashes-11.jpg', 'Russian Lashes', 'In Russian lashes, more than one extension is applied to one natural lash by fanning them to make them appear like more lashes are growing from one stem. These lashes fall out with our natural hair growth cycle and they can last up to 6 weeks with proper maintenance. Russian lashes can be done to achieve a fuller but natural enhancement or a dramatic look.', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 27px; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold;\">What are the benefits of Russian lashes?</b></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><li>Russian Lashes give your lashes a more defined and fuller look</li><li>Russian Lashes are extremely lightweight and can’t be felt when applied</li><li>Russian Lashes are apt for special occasions and holidays or if you want a natural enhancement</li><li>If you want to avoid wearing mascara every day, this treatment is for you. It helps you to say no to clumping, and smudging mascara</li><li>You can opt either for a natural or for a full-on glam look</li><li>With proper maintenance these lashes can last several weeks</li></ul>', '<p><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">1. Is there anything I need to do before my lash treatment? (Pre-care)</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A.</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><li>We highly recommend cleaning your lashes before arriving for your scheduled appointment</li><li>Please avoid using oil-based products on and around the eye area</li><li>Get a shower before your appointment as you will not be suggested to get the lashes wet at all for 24 hours after your treatment</li><li>If you use contact lenses, you will be asked to remove them during your treatment and therefore, don’t forget to bring your lens case and solution with you</li></ul><p><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">2. How old must I be to have this done?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. From age of 16+ you can receive this service.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">3. How long do Russian Lashes last?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Ideally, they can last up to 4 to 5 weeks, depending on the condition of your natural lashes, you post treatment care or cleanliness and the natural oil production of the eye area. We recommend to refill lash in every 2 weeks for long lasting results. You can also individually replace the lashes which have fallen out.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">4. How long will this treatment take?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Your appointment will take approximately 1.5 hours. if you opt for the glamour look this will take longer than the usual time stated above.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">5. Do I need a patch test?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Yes , if you have not had semi permanent lashes or Russian lashes done from us before , you are required to come for a patch test 24/48 hours prior to your appointment. If you are a regular client and we have your semi permanent lash or Russian lash extension history within 6 months registered in our system, you do not require a patch test if there is no change in your medical history.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">5. I don’t want my lashes to be too long. Is this suitable for me?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Yes, this is suitable for you as lashes come in all lengths. Therefore, you can choose to have a fuller look but natural length.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">6. Does this hurt?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. No. This is a closed eye treatment, and you should feel relaxed during your treatment.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">7. I wear contact lenses. Can I have this done?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Yes, this is suitable for you. Although we do recommend removing your lenses for the duration of the treatment.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">8. Can I apply mascara on my false lashes?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Applying mascara can give you a dramatic look, however if you do not apply any products on your lashes, they can last longer.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">9. Can I get the lashes wet?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Try not to get your lashes wet. Once the lashes get wet, it will be hard to maintain its curl and shape.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">10. I have an eye infection is this suitable for me?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. If you are suffering from any eye infection, you shouldn’t undergo this treatment. If you have a stye or other infection, inside or at the edge of your eyelid, they can become inflamed and painful due to this treatment. You should inform your therapist beforehand about any such concern and seek medical advice before undergoing any treatment.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">11. What should I do after my treatment? Are there any restrictions? (Aftercare)</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A.</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><li>For 48 hours avoid sauna, steam, showers, or hot baths</li><li>Please be gentle with your lashes</li><li>Please avoid using oil-based products on the eye area</li><li>Please do not rub or pull your lashes out</li><li>Do not use waterproof mascara or make up remover as this will affect the bonding of the lashes</li><li>Never pull off the eyelash extensions as this will pull out your natural lashes too</li><li>Be gentle with the extensions and avoid tugging and getting them caught on clothes and towels</li></ul>', '2023-03-29 09:51:42', '2023-03-29 09:51:42'),
(42, 'lashes', 'LASH LIFT AND TINT', '202303290954lash-lift-11.jpg', 'Lash Lift', 'Lash Lift is a perming method which uses silicone shields. This technique is used to lift the lash from the root, and it can lift, straighten, or curl your lashes upwards creating a volumized look to your own natural lashes. This treatment is combined with a tinting service to give you a volumized and gorgeous mascara look.', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 27px; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold;\">What are the benefits of lash lift?</b></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><li>This treatment enhances your natural lashes without the hassle of any ongoing maintenance</li><li>There is no need to wear mascara for a few weeks after this treatment as it includes lash tint</li><li>This treatment will make your natural lashes look fuller, thicker, and longer</li><li>The curls in your lashes last around 5 weeks, depending on the health of your lashes and how you maintain them</li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px;\">If you are a hay fever sufferer and prone to itchy or watery eyes, this treatment is beneficial for you.</p></ul>', '<p><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">1. Is there anything I need to do before my lash lift treatment? (Pre-care)</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A.</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><li>We highly recommend cleaning your lashes before arriving for your scheduled appointment</li><li>Please avoid using oil-based products on and around the eye area</li><li>Get a shower before your appointment as you will not be suggested to get the lashes wet at all for 24 hours after your treatment</li><li>If you use contact lenses, you will be asked to remove them during your treatment and therefore, don’t forget to bring your lens case and solution with you</li></ul><p><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">2. How old must I be to have this done?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. From age of 16+ you can receive this service.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">3. How long does Lash Lift last for?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Ideally, it can last up to 6 weeks, but this can vary from person to person. No maintenance appointments are required for this treatment. We recommend repeating this process every 6 to 8 weeks to lift the new hair growth as well. With the use of harsh products and heat or if you are a swimmer, you may find your lashes are dropping or weakening prematurely.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">4. How long will this treatment take?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Your appointment will take approximately 60 minutes.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">5. Do I need a patch test?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Yes, if you have not had Lash Lift before or with elegance salons within the last 6 months, please pop in for a patch test 48 hours prior to your appointment. If you are a regular client for Lash Lift with us, you do not require a patch test if there is no change in your medical history.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">5. Is this treatment safe?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Yes, lashes are lifted on to specially made eye pads before applying the products.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">6. Does this hurt?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. This treatment is done with your eyes being closed and it is painless. Clients find this procedure to be relaxing.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">7. I wear contact lenses can I have this done?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Yes, this is suitable for you. Although we do recommend removing your lenses for the duration of the treatment.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">8. Can I apply mascara on my lashes?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Yes, you can apply mascara after 48 hours, which can give a dramatic look. However, if you do not apply any products on your lashes, they can stay longer.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">9. Does lash lift damage your natural lashes?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. No, but we suggest following the aftercare for the treatment stated below.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">10. I have an eye infection is this suitable for me?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. If you are suffering from any eye infection, you shouldn’t undergo this treatment. If you have a stye or other infection, inside or at the edge of your eyelid, they can become inflamed and painful due to this treatment. You should inform your therapist beforehand about any such concern and seek medical advice before undergoing any treatment.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">11. What should I do after my treatment? Are there any restrictions? (Aftercare)</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A.</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><li>For 48 hours avoid getting your lashes wet</li><li>Do not use harsh products on your lashes</li><li>• For 48 hours please avoid sauna, swimming, and steam as this will weaken the effect of your treatment</li><li>Do not use eyelash curlers and waterproof mascara</li><li>Avoid any facial treatments for 48 hours</li><li>Use gentle soap free products around the eyes and use a lash nourishing serum daily</li></ul>', '2023-03-29 09:54:06', '2023-03-29 09:54:06'),
(43, 'nails', 'BASIC MANICURES AND PEDICURES', '202303290956basic-manicure-pedicure-11.jpg', 'Basic Manicures and Pedicures', 'A manicure refers to the curation and care of a client\'s hands and a pedicure refers to the curation and care of a client\'s feet. This includes skincare, nail care, and artificial nail enhancements that can be customized to a variety of preferences.', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 27px; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold;\">What are the benefits of Manicures and Pedicures?</b></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 27px; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><li>Deep clean for your nails, as well as ensuring that they look great</li><li>Removal of dead skill cells, which is an essential part of encouraging new skin cell growth</li><li>Protect your nail health on an ongoing basis</li><li>Increase blood flow , improve joint mobility and help to reduce swelling and pain</li><li>Incredibly relaxing experience</li></ul>', '<p><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">1. How is it done?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. manicure and pedicure consist of filing and shaping the free edge of nails, pushing and clipping (with a cuticle pusher and cuticle nippers) any non-living tissue (but limited to the cuticle and hangnails), and the application of fingernail polish. You can also upgrade to French polish or hand massage with an additional cost.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">2. How long will manicure and pedicure take?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Your appointment will ideally take around 15- 20 minutes for basic manicure and 20-25 minutes for basic pedicure.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">3. Does a manicure hurt?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Manicures and Pedicures shouldn\'t hurt or damage your nails.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">4. What\'s the difference between a luxury manicure and a basic manicure?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. The number one focus of a basic manicure is your nails. A luxury manicure is typically a longer service focused on stress relief and relaxation. A luxury manicure typically lasts longer than a regular manicure, and more emphasis is placed on the overall experience, rather than hand maintenance.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">5. Should I trim my nails before a pedicure?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. If you\'re doing a pedicure, then no, don\'t trim them. When the nail comes back in, it\'ll be ingrown. You should trim them straight across, not rounded.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">6. How long does standard polish last for?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Normal nail polish usually lasts up to 5 days with proper care and is a great choice for temporary or short one-off occasions. If that’s too short of period for you then we recommend you book a gel manicure which can last up to two weeks.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">7. How often you should get manicures and pedicures?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 27px; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">It depends on your lifestyle and preference. The faster your nails grow and the more abuse they withstand and if you prefer perfect polish and medium to long nails, you’ll need a manicure once a week. If you favour shorter nails for a more active lifestyle, you may need a professional manicure only every two weeks.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Overall, we’d recommend on average every two weeks – maximum three weeks!</p>', '2023-03-29 09:56:46', '2023-03-29 09:56:46'),
(44, 'nails', 'GEL MANICURES AND PEDICURES', '202303290959gel-nails-11.jpg', 'Gel Nails', 'Gel polish is a thick consistency liquid, which is applied to the natural nail and cured under UV light. Gel nails last longer than normal nail varnish leaving your nails shiny and strong for up to 14 days.', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 27px; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold;\">What are the benefits of Gel Nails?</b></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><li>Gel nails dry quicker under UV light, so there’s no need to worry about smudging them</li><li>Long lasting- It can last up to 14 days without fading and is scratch free</li><li>If your nails are weak or prone to splitting, gel polish gives your nails added protection</li><li>Gel nails look and feel natural, as the gel is applied in thin layers</li></ul>', '<p><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">1. How are Gel Nails done?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Your therapist will firstly carry out a consultation with you to discuss your needs and the end results/colour you are looking to achieve. The treatment is done by firstly prepping your nails with dry manicure technique, then two coats of gel polish is applied in thin layers for a natural finish, which cures and hardens under UV light and can last up to a good two weeks.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">2. Is there anything I need to do before my treatment? Pre-care?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Your nails must be a normal length for this treatment. Extremely short nails will be difficult to do, also they will not last very long at all. Please make sure your nails are clean and free from any debris, and decide how you want your nails to look, we will try our best!</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">3. How old must I be to have this done?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. From age of 11+ you can receive this service with consent of parent or guardian.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">4. How long do Gel Nails last for?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Gel Nails can last up to 2 weeks. We recommend you have your gel nails removed professionally to avoid damage to the nail bed. Gel nails can be removed and reapplied every two-three weeks and change of colour.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">5. How long will this treatment take?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Your appointment will ideally take around 20-30 minutes.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">5. What should I be doing after my treatment, are there any restrictions?Aftercare</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A.</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><li>For 48 hours, please avoid swimming, sauna, steam as the gel takes time to bond and harden further to adhere to your nail bed</li><li>Do not use your nails as tools this will damage and weaken them</li><li>Avoid using nail polish remover containing acetone</li><li>Wear gloves when performing household chores, gardening and use of chemicals</li><li>Keep up with maintenance appointments to keep your nails looking their best</li><li>Apply cuticle oil daily to prolong enhancements durability and flexibility and cuticle softness</li></ul>', '2023-03-29 09:59:20', '2023-03-29 09:59:20');
