(45, 'nails', 'ACRYLICS EXTENSIONS', '202303291002acrylics-11.jpg', 'Acrylics Extensions', 'Acrylic extensions are nail enhancements, which is set using a combination of a liquid monomer and powder polymer. Enhancements are created as an option for clients wishing to transform their natural nails instantly into beautiful strong nails.', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 27px; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold;\">What are the benefits of Acrylic extensions?</b></p><li style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Acrylic extensions are very popular treatment at elegance salons, as they are long lasting</li><li style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">These enhancements are great for protecting weak nails and they prevent you from biting nails (if you are a nail biter and want to grow your nails)</li><li style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">The extensions are natural looking, and you have plenty of colours and designs to choose from</li>', '<p><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">1. How are Acrylic Extensions done?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Your therapist will firstly carry out a consultation with you to discuss your needs and the end results you are looking to achieve. The treatment is done by combining liquid monomer and powder polymer to make an acrylic nail. This paste is applied onto your natural nail and tip which hardens over time and can last up to a good couple of weeks.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">2. Is there anything I need to do before my treatment? (Pre-care)</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Your nails must be at a normal length for this treatment. If you have extremely short nails, it will be difficult to do the treatment and in that case the extension will not last very long at all. Please make sure your nails are clean and free from any debris, polish, and oils. From our various options, you can select your desired nail look and we will achieve that for you.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">3. How old must I be to have this done?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. From age of 12+ you can receive this service with consent of parent or guardian.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">4. How long do Acrylic Extensions last for?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Acrylic extensions can last up to 2 weeks. We recommend refills every 2 weeks for coverage of the regrowth and to maintain your nails and for longevity of your enhancements (at this point you can even choose a different colour!).</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">5. I don’t want my nails too long; I desire a natural length. Can I still have these done?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Yes, the therapist will carry out a consultation and the treatment will be done step by step. You will be in charge of your shape, length, colour and design.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">5. How long will this treatment take?</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A. Your appointment will ideally take around 60-70 minutes.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"font-weight: bold; color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">6. What should I be doing after my treatment, are there any restrictions?Aftercare</b><br style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">A.</span></p><ul style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><li>For 48 hours, please avoid swimming, sauna, steam as the acrylic takes time to bond and harden further to adhere to your nail bed</li><li>Do not use your nails as tools this will damage and weaken them</li><li>Avoid using nail polish remover containing acetone</li><li>Wear gloves when performing household chores, gardening and use of chemicals</li><li>If your break a nail or if it comes off, please do not try to glue it back on yourself this could lead to infections</li><li>Book maintenance appointments to keep your nails on-point and perfect</li><li>• Apply cuticle oil daily to soften cuticle, prolong enhancement’s durability and flexibility</li></ul>', '2023-03-29 10:02:18', '2023-03-29 10:02:18');

